CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Continental African man wearing traditional clothing shaking hands with Jessie Vann, surrounded by others, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence, in Office of the Mayor, City County Building
